{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 349411, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以前清华提出过，北京市交通局要求以二校门前面清华路打通为市政道路作为条件（即颐和园路~清华西路~清华东路~大屯路打通），thu校园分为南校区北校区，故作废。红绿灯不是学校想安就能安的。", "timestamp": 1600067770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349415, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 交通局这条件好奇怪→_→", "timestamp": 1600067834, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349417, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 15号线计划就是要沿着这个路线通过的，清华不同意，因此断头在“清华东路西口”站（15号线设计西端起点为西苑站）", "timestamp": 1600067890, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349420, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "交通局没校友吗", "timestamp": 1600067977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349421, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "车技太差就多练 别总想着改变环境", "timestamp": 1600068036, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349426, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "安装红绿灯还有权限的问题吗 难道不是有钱买一个装上就行", "timestamp": 1600068119, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349432, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "安排专人指挥交通就行啊", "timestamp": 1600068197, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349433, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 人那么多车技再好也白搭", "timestamp": 1600068216, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349436, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 这不是车技问题吧，路口堵死的时候车技好就能飞过去吗，不看路的超速的电动自行车来了车技好就能躲得掉吗", "timestamp": 1600068229, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349438, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 必须通过交通局批准才能安（不然基本上和违建一个待遇）", "timestamp": 1600068243, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 北京市这方面规定比较严格，必须是市政道路才能安装红绿灯。在北京这些年，还真没看见哪个类似thu这种大院有红绿灯配置", "timestamp": 1600068408, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349462, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 安装红绿灯的行政许可? 我没检索到法律依据。倒是有规定说如果该安的不安，出事了负有相关职责的单位要负责赔", "timestamp": 1600068559, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349477, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这个剧情我猜是这样，学校自己不想出钱装，找交管局/交通委，他们就说这不是我管的路为什么要我出钱，于是就没人出钱，就没人装", "timestamp": 1600068865, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349485, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实至少找一个疏导的人也可以", "timestamp": 1600068916, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349505, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 70490, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "放心啦 最多一个礼拜就不堵车了（", "timestamp": 1600069459, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 70490, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "强烈建议六教附近装红绿灯", "timestamp": 1600067630, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782619, "url": "", "vote": {}}}